headline: PepsiCo, Unilever, and other Major Retail, Food, and Beverage Companies Launch "STEP up for Agriculture" Initiative
summary: Today, leading retail and global food and beverage companies including PepsiCo (NASDAQ: PEP) and Unilever announce the launch of Supporting Trusted Engagement and Partnership (STEP) up for Agriculture (STEP up for Ag), a pre-competitive initiative designed to strengthen the capacity and sustainability of farmer-facing support organizations across North America.

headline: Buy Wide-Moat PepsiCo: Activist Involvement Is Icing On The Cake
summary: PepsiCo has underperformed the S&P 500 and key peers over 5- and 10-year periods, with notably lower total returns. Read why I rate PEP stock a Buy now.
